OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FITV News has learnt that the family of
OL,7,Fa woman who died after being
OL,8,Fmisdiagnosed by a physician associate
OL,9,Fhas won the backing of the BMA in a
OL,10,Flegal fight for better regulation, as
OL,11,FITV News' Rebecca Barry reports
OL,13,FWords by Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,14,FBarry and Health and Science Producer
OL,15,FPhilip Sime
