OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FITV News can exclusively reveal that
OL,7,Fthe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,8,Fis joining legal action being brought
OL,9,Fby a bereaved family against the
OL,10,Fmedical regulator over the role of
OL,11,Fphysician associates in the NHS.
OL,13,FThe parents of 30-year-old Emily
OL,14,FChesterton, who died from a pulmonary
OL,15,Fembolism after she was misdiagnosed by
OL,16,Fa physician associate, accuse the
OL,17,FGeneral Medical Council (GMC) of
OL,18,Fputting patients at risk by failing to
OL,19,Fdistinguish properly between the role
OL,20,Fof doctors and medical associates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
