OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FThey are joining a legal case against
OL,7,Fthe GMC alongside the campaign group
OL,8,FAnaesthetists United.
OL,10,FThe doctors' union, the BMA, will
OL,11,Ffinancially support the case.
OL,13,FPhysician associates (PAs) and
OL,14,Fanaesthesia associates (AAs) should
OL,15,Fwork under the supervision of doctors
OL,16,Fin hospitals and GP practices.
OL,18,FThey must complete a three-year
OL,19,Fhealth, biomedical or science
OL,20,Fundergraduate degree, followed by two
OL,21,Fyears of postgraduate medical training.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
