OL,6,FThey can take medical histories and
OL,7,Fhelp to diagnose patients, but can't
OL,8,Fprescribe or order x-rays.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThere are around 3,500 physician
OL,16,Fassociates and anaesthesia associates
OL,17,Fworking in the NHS in England.
OL,19,FThe health service's Long Term
OL,20,FWorkforce Plan aims to increase that
OL,21,Fto 10,000 by 2037.
