OL,6,FAhead of this expansion, there are
OL,7,Fgrowing calls for the GMC to create a
OL,8,Fnational scope of practice, which
OL,9,Fclearly sets out the tasks that PAs
OL,10,Fand AAs should and should not be
OL,11,Fallowed to undertake.
OL,13,FEmily Chesterton's parents, Marion and
OL,14,FBrendan, spoke to ITV News as they
OL,15,Fjoined the legal action.
OL,17,F"We're just trying our best for
OL,18,FEmily," Marion Chesterton said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
