OL,6,F"I just want to help other people and
OL,7,Fget something good out of this because
OL,8,Fshe was such a beautiful person. She
OL,9,Fwouldn't want anyone to go through
OL,10,Fwhat we have been through. She has
OL,11,Flost her life and she had such a
OL,12,Fwonderful life ahead of her," Marion
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We don't want other families to go
OL,16,Fthrough what we go through and we
OL,17,Fdon't want other Emilys who are
OL,18,Fcollateral damage for this push to put
OL,19,FPAs and AAs into the NHS," Brendan
OL,20,FChesterton said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
