OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FBMA Council Chair, Professor Philip
OL,7,FBanfield, says there is a "lack of
OL,8,Flimits" to what physician associates
OL,9,Fcan and can't do.
OL,11,F"As a doctor, I have things that I can
OL,12,Fand can't do. My practice is regulated
OL,13,Fby the GMC," Professor Banfield said.
OL,15,F"What we're seeing is physician
OL,16,Fassociates being placed in situations
OL,17,Fwhich are unsafe for them and unsafe
OL,18,Ffor patients," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
