OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Dr Richard Marks, co-
OL,7,Ffounder of Anaesthetists United said:
OL,8,F"We think the public would be shocked
OL,9,Fthat, not only are there no national
OL,10,Frules saying what associates can and
OL,11,Fcan't do, but they're not even
OL,12,Fplanning on introducing any so we want
OL,13,Fto set that straight."
OL,15,FThe GMC has an overarching duty to
OL,16,Fprotect the public, says Dr Richard
OL,17,FMarks
OL,19,FAt the Royal Berkshire Hospital in
OL,20,FReading, they have 46 physician
OL,21,Fassociates across 16 specialities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
