OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News on a ward on
OL,7,FTuesday, Chief Medical Officer Dr
OL,8,FJanet Lippett, said they are a valued
OL,9,Fand vital part of the team, and that
OL,10,Fthey work under the supervision of
OL,11,Fqualified and experienced doctors.
OL,13,FDr Lippett described the current
OL,14,Fdebate around the use of physician
OL,15,Fassociates as "toxic".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
