OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,F"These bright, young, enthusiastic
OL,7,Findividuals went to university to
OL,8,Flearn their trade, just as I did as a
OL,9,Fdoctor," Dr Lippett said. "Properly
OL,10,Fsupervised, properly nurtured, they
OL,11,Freally are a welcome addition to the
OL,12,Fteam."
OL,14,FThe GMC will start regulating
OL,15,Fphysician associates from December
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FResponses from the General Medical
OL,19,FCouncil, the Department of Health and
OL,20,FSocial Care and NHS England
