OL,6,F"Regulation is a vital step towards
OL,7,Fstrengthening both patient safety and
OL,8,Fpublic trust in these professions. It
OL,9,Fwill help provide assurance to
OL,10,Fpatients, employers and colleagues
OL,11,Fthat PAs and AAs have the right level
OL,12,Fof education and training, meet the
OL,13,Fstandards that we expect of the
OL,14,Fprofessions we regulate and that they
OL,15,Fcan be held to account if serious
OL,16,Fconcerns are raised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
