OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,F"Employers also need to make sure
OL,7,Fthere are appropriate governance
OL,8,Fstructures in place, to make sure that
OL,9,FPAs and AAs are working under
OL,10,Fsupervision."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care said:
OL,15,F"This is a tragic case and our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with Emily Chesterton's
OL,17,Ffamily and friends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
