OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,F"We are clear that physician
OL,7,Fassociates should be supporting, not
OL,8,Freplacing, doctors and should receive
OL,9,Fthe appropriate level of supervision
OL,10,Fby healthcare organisations.
OL,12,F"The NHS has issued clear guidance on
OL,13,Fthe deployment of physician associates
OL,14,Fand anaesthesia associates in the NHS
OL,15,Fand we expect trusts to follow this."
OL,17,FAn NHS England spokesperson said:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
