OL,3,CBMA backs family suing regulator over
OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,F"The NHS has always been clear about
OL,7,Fthe role medical associates play in
OL,8,Fsupporting clinical teams to provide
OL,9,Fhigh quality care for patients ` they
OL,10,Fare not replacements for doctors, but
OL,11,Fsupport teams with specific tasks they
OL,12,Fare trained to do, under supervision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
