OL,4,Cthe role of NHS physician associates
OL,6,F"We know that the confidence of the
OL,7,Fpublic and the medical community is
OL,8,Fabsolutely essential as we develop an
OL,9,FNHS workforce that is fit for the
OL,10,Ffuture, which is why the NHS has
OL,11,Fissued updated guidance on the
OL,12,Fappropriate deployment of these roles,
OL,13,Fand will continue to work together
OL,14,Fwith government and medical and
OL,15,Fpatient groups to provide clarity on
OL,16,Fthese roles for patients and the
OL,17,Fpublic, ahead of the GMC regulation
OL,18,Fcoming into effect at the end of the
OL,19,Fyear."
